Database Readme

This file explains how the database system will work and how it will interact with the webpage.

The mysql databases is called SpoilerAlert. Within the PHP page we will have a config page that uses this.

There will be a table for Movies, Video Games, and Books.

Each table will have the following collumns. 

id      title           spoiler

Within the php we will have the command select spoiler from ("title"). 

Will update as I complete database. 
